%20stand%20between%20700%20and%20750%20metric%20tons%20in%202024%2C%20the%20lowest%20since%202020%20and%20down%20from%20last%20year's%20761%20tons%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cost%20Of%20Sleeping%20On%20AI%3A%20Samsung%20Loses%201%2F3rd%20Of%20Its%20Value%20In%204%20Months%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20Samsung%20Electronics%20Co.%20looked%20primed%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20global%20AI%20boom%3A%20profits%20were%20surging%20and%20its%20stock%20was%20rising%20toward%20an%20all-time%20high.%20Now%2C%20South%20Korea's%20biggest%20company%20has%20become%20a%20stark%20example%20of%20how%20quickly%20fortunes%20can%20turn%20in%20an%20industry%20where%20the%20spoils%20go%20to%20those%20who%20maintain%20a%20technological%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20concerns%20mount%20that%20the%20company%20is%20losing%20out%20to%20smaller%20rival%20SK%20Hynix%20Inc.%20in%20AI%20memory%20and%20failing%20to%20gain%20on%20Taiwan%20Semiconductor%20Manufacturing%20Co.%20in%20outsourced%20chipmaking%2C%20Samsung%20shares%20have%20tumbled%2032%25%20from%20this%20year's%20peak%20on%20July%209.%20The%20company%20has%20lost%20%24122%20billion%20of%20market%20value%20in%20that%20span%2C%20more%20than%20any%20other%20chipmaker%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamsung%20has%20promised%20an%20overhaul%20to%20regain%20competitiveness%2C%20but%20international%20money%20managers%20including%20Pictet%20Asset%20Management%20Ltd.%20and%20Janus%20Henderson%20Investors%20SP%20Ltd.%20are%20unconvinced%20a%20turnaround%20is%20imminent.%20Overseas%20investors%20have%20sold%20about%20%2410.7%20billion%20worth%20of%20the%20South%20Korean%20company's%20shares%20on%20a%20net%20basis%20since%20the%20end%20of%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20more%20than%20halved%20our%20position%20in%20Samsung%20over%20the%20last%20few%20months%20-%20it%20was%20the%20largest%20position%20in%20our%20strategy%20in%20July%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sat%20Duhra%2C%20a%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Janus%20Henderson%20Investors%20SP%20in%20Singapore.%20While%20Duhra%20said%20the%20shares%20have%20fallen%20to%20an%20attractive%20valuation%2C%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Bno%20intention%26quot%3B%20to%20buy%20them%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFading%20Fast%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmartphones%20and%20other%20consumer%20electronics%20still%20account%20for%20the%20biggest%20share%20of%20Samsung's%20sales%2C%20but%20semiconductors%20have%20been%20contributing%20the%20most%20profit%20in%20recent%20years.%20With%20the%20recent%20crisis%20in%20its%20chip%20business%2C%20the%20Suwon-based%20company%20issued%20a%20rare%20apology%20to%20investors%20earlier%20this%20month%20for%20disappointing%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20story%20highlights%20how%20AI%20is%20the%20key%20factor%20minting%20winners%20and%20losers%20in%20today's%20chip%20sector.%20While%20foreign%20investors%20have%20led%20an%20exodus%20from%20Samsung%2C%20Nvidia%20Corp.%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20companies.%20TSMC%2C%20the%20key%20maker%20of%20chips%20designed%20by%20Nvidia%20and%20Apple%20Inc.%2C%20has%20added%20over%20%24330%20billion%20in%20market%20value%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThings%20went%20south%20for%20Samsung%20quickly.%20Its%20stock%20flirted%20with%20a%20record%20high%20after%20it%20posted%20a%2015-fold%20surge%20in%20operating%20profit%20for%20the%20June%20quarter.%20As%20recently%20as%20August%2C%20investors%20were%20optimistic%20it%20could%20win%20more%20business%20supplying%20Nvidia%20with%20high-bandwidth%20memory%20to%20work%20alongside%20AI%20processors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20hope%20has%20been%20snuffed%20out%20with%20the%20company%20admitting%20delays%20with%20its%20latest-generation%20HBM%20chips%20in%20early%20October%2C%20soon%20after%20SK%20Hynix%20said%20it%20had%20begun%20volume%20production.%20Meanwhile%2C%20US%20rival%20Micron%20Technology%20Inc.%20is%20stepping%20up%20efforts%20in%20HBM%20as%20well%2C%20and%20has%20reported%20strong%20demand%20for%20its%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamsung%20is%20%26quot%3Blosing%20its%20technology%20leadership%20in%20the%20semiconductor%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Young%20Jae%20Lee%2C%20London-based%20senior%20investment%20manager%20of%20the%20global%20emerging%20markets%20high-dividend%20team%20at%20Pictet%20Asset%20Management.%20%26quot%3BTechnology%20leadership%20is%20difficult%20to%20regain%20in%20the%20short%20term%20by%20nature%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20firm%20has%20been%20reducing%20its%20Samsung%20holding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EManagement%20Issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20its%20lag%20in%20AI%20memory%2C%20Samsung%20has%20struggled%20with%20a%20costly%2C%20yearslong%20effort%20to%20close%20the%20gap%20with%20TSMC%20in%20foundry%20business.%20Like%20Intel%20Corp.%20-%20which%20has%20run%20into%20similar%20difficulty%20with%20plans%20to%20expand%20its%20outsourced%20chipmaking%20operations%20-%20the%20Korean%20firm%20is%20now%20moving%20to%20cut%20jobs%20and%20make%20other%20efforts%20to%20stop%20the%20bleeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamsung%20is%20holding%20a%20conference%20call%20on%20Thursday%20after%20it%20releases%20detailed%20third-quarter%20earnings.%20Among%20points%20to%20watch%20is%20an%20expected%20management%20reshuffle%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20amid%20ongoing%20uncertainty%20over%20company%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJay%20Y%20Lee%20-%20a%20grandson%20of%20Samsung's%20founder%20who%20was%20appointed%20executive%20chairman%20two%20years%20ago%20-%20was%20acquitted%20of%20stock%20manipulation%20charges%20in%20February%20after%20years%20of%20legal%20issues.%20Three%20months%20later%2C%20the%20company%20unexpectedly%20replaced%20its%20semiconductor%20division%20head%20with%20Jun%20Young-hyun%2C%20a%20memory%20chip%20veteran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManagement%20may%20have%20its%20work%20cut%20out%20for%20it%20in%20trying%20to%20win%20back%20investors%2C%20even%20with%20stock%20valuations%20near%20a%20record%20low%20and%20technical%20indicators%20flashing%20oversold%20signals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20see%20much%20is%20changing%20with%20the%20Samsung%20executives%20and%20engineers%20are%20leaving%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Park%20Jinho%2C%20head%20of%20equity%20investment%20at%20NH-Amundi%20Asset%20Management%20Co.%20in%20Seoul.%20Park%20reduced%20Samsung%20to%20underweight%20from%20neutral%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20second%20quarter%20and%20added%20SK%20Hynix%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730273940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-11%2Ft8liv6p8_samsung-generic_625x300_15_November_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcost-of-sleeping-on-ai-samsung-loses-over-1-4th-of-its-value-in-4-months-6906197%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Just%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20Samsung%20looked%20primed%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20global%20AI%20boom.%20Now%2C%20it%20has%20become%20a%20stark%20example%20of%20how%20quickly%20fortunes%20can%20turn%20in%20an%20industry%20where%20the%20spoils%20go%20to%20those%20who%20maintain%20a%20technological%20edge.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%20Retentions%20Live%3A%20Suspense%20On%20Rohit%20But%20MI%20Set%20To%20Retain%20These%204%20Stars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIPL%202025%20Retentions%2C%20Live%20Updates%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECricket%20fans%20around%20the%20world%20are%20eagerly%20waiting%20for%20the%20a