's%20quotas%26quot%3B%2C%20referring%20to%20more%20than%20one%20instance%20of%20BJP%20leaders%20contesting%20seats%20for%20the%20Shinde%20Sena%20or%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20misunderstanding%20between%20us%20(but)%20Mahayuti%20members%20are%20fighting%20amongst%20themselves.%20They%20are%20fighting%20from%20each%20other's%20quotas...%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20fighting%20under%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20symbols.%20It%20is%20the%20BJP%20that%20is%20fighting%20alone...%20Shinde%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20are%20finished.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20also%20stressed%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%2C%20in%20the%20MVA%2C%20have%20given%20equal%20treatment%20to%20all...%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20comment%20seen%20by%20many%20as%20countering%20criticism%20of%20the%20party%20after%20the%20Haryana%20election%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20widely%20expected%20to%20record%20a%20comfortable%20win%20in%20the%20heartland%20state%2C%20raced%20into%20a%20big%20early%20lead%20as%20votes%20were%20counted%20October%208%2C%20but%20slipped%20to%20defeat%20by%20the%20BJP's%20late%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party's%20allies%2C%20most%20notably%20the%20Thackeray%20Sena%2C%20were%20angered%20by%20what%20they%20said%20was%20the%20Congress'%20failure%20to%20accommodate%20smaller%20and%20regional%20partners.%20The%20Thackeray%20Sena's%20jabs%20-%20published%20in%20party%20mouthpiece%20Saamana%20-%20drew%20an%20immediate%20response%20from%20the%20Congress'%20Maharashtra%20office%2C%20which%20said%20it%20valued%20their%20allies%20and%20would%20not%20act%20as%20the%20Haryana%20unit%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-haryana-assembly-election-results-shiv-sena-editorial-saamana-arrogant-overconfident-congress-allies-on-warpath-after-haryana-loss-6749949%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BArrogant%2C%20Overconf