t%2C%20Slammed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECanada's%20opposition%20leader%20Pierre%20Poilievre%20has%20cancelled%20Diwali%20celebrations%20that%20were%20scheduled%20to%20take%20place%20at%20Parliament%20Hill%20in%20Ottawa%2C%20drawing%20severe%20backlash%20from%20the%20Indian%20community.%20The%20move%20comes%20amid%20diplomatic%20tensions%20and%20worsening%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20-%20especially%20after%20Canada%20alleged%20Indian%20diplomats%20were%20involved%20in%20targeting%20pro-Khalistanis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20organiser%20of%20the%20Diwali%20event%2C%20Shiv%20Bhasker%20-%20who%20is%20also%20the%20president%20of%20Overseas%20Friends%20of%20India%20Canada%20(OFIC)%20-%20they%20did%20not%20receive%20any%20explanation%20for%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bdiscriminatory%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Binsensitive%26quot%3B%20act%2C%20Mr%20Bhasker%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Mr%20Poilievre%2C%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20event%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20joyous%20occasion%20to%20honour%20Diwali%2C%20a%20festival%20that%20is%20not%20only%20deeply%20significant%20to%20the%20Indo-Canadian%20community%20but%20also%20emblematic%20of%20the%20multicultural%20spirit%20that%20Canada%20prides%20itself%20on.%20However%2C%20the%20sudden%20withdrawal%20of%20political%20leaders%20from%20this%20event%2C%20prompted%20by%20the%20current%20diplomatic%20situation%20between%20Canada%20and%20India%2C%20has%20left%20us%20feeling%20betrayed%20and%20unjustly%20singled%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20set%20to%20be%20hosted%20by%20Conservative%20MP%20Todd%20Doherty%20on%20October%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20developments%2C%20while%20deeply%20concerning%2C%20should%20never%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20unfair%20treatment%20of%20Canadians%20of%20Indian%20descent%2C%20who%20have%20no%20connection%20to%20the%20actions%20or%20decisions%20of%20a%20foreign%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20event%20organiser%2C%20racism%20and%20discrimination%20are%20%26quot%3Bthriving%26quot%3B%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20latest%20development%20has%20laid%20bare%20the%20systemic%20biases%20that%20still%20exist.%20Our%20politicians%2C%20by%20recusing%20themselves%20from%20these%20cultural%20celebrations%2C%20have%20sent%20a%20message-intentionally%20or%20not-that%20we%2C%20as%20Canadians%20of%20Indian%20heritage%20are%20not%20fully%20part%20of%20this%20nation%2C%20that%20we%20are%20somehow%20less%20Canadian%20because%20of%20our%20ancestral%20ties%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20community%20has%20demanded%20an%20apology%20from%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20rival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20than%20just%20words%2C%20we%20expect%20a%20clear%20and%20actionable%20course%20of%20action%20to%20be%20laid%20out%20to%20address%20the%20systemic%20racism%20and%20bias%20that%20led%20to%20this%20decision.%20It%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20offer%20empty%20platitudes%20or%20generalized%20statements%20of%20support%20-%20we%20need%20to%20see%20real%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20Bhasker%2C%20the%20letter%20represents%20the%20collective%20voice%20of%20the%20Indo-Canadian%20community%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20refuse%20to%20let%20the%20actions%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bforeign%20government%20dictate%26quot%3B%20how%20they%20are%20perceived%20and%20treated%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20backlash%2C%20the%20office%20of%20Overseas%20Friends%20of%20India%20Canada%20issued%20an%20apology%20for%20cancelling%20the%20event%20and%20organised%20another%20celebration%20on%20November%2023.%20The%20event%20will%20take%20place%20at%20Cedar%20Hill%20Golf%20and%20Country%20Club%20in%20Nepean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20similar%20Diwali%20celebration%20was%20held%20at%20Parliament%20Hill%20in%20Canada%2C%20hosted%20by%20Indo-Canadian%20parliamentarian%20Chandrasekhar%20Arya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia-Canada%20diplomatic%20relationship%20has%20been%20spiralling%20downward%20over%20repeated%20and%20unsubstantiated%20claims%20by%20PM%20Trudeau%20-%20that%20%26quot%3Bagents%26quot%3B%20of%20Delhi%20conspire%20with%20criminal%20gangs%2C%20including%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20outfit%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Btarget%20(the)%20South%20Asians%26quot%3B%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20emphatically%20junked%20links%20to%20his%20death%2C%20rubbishing%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmalicious%26quot%3B%20and%20pointing%20out%2C%20repeatedly%2C%20that%20neither%20Mr%20Trudeau%20nor%20his%20government%20have%20shared%20any%20hard%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730273280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F5tkq1p18_pierre-poilievre_625x300_30_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finsensitive-act-canada-opposition-leader-pierre-poilievre-cancels-diwali-event-slammed-justin-trudeau-india-canada-diplomatic-relations-6906367%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canada's%20opposition%20leader%20Pierre%20Poilievre%20has%20cancelled%20Diwali%20celebrations%20that%20were%20scheduled%20to%20take%20place%20at%20Parliament%20Hill%20in%20Ottawa.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gold%20demand%20surpasses%20%24100%20billion%20globally%20as%20western%20investors%20rush%20in%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730273095000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgold-demand-surpasses-100-billion-globally-as-western-investors-rush-in-124103000472_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gold%20-%20which%20s