harmila%20over%20an%20inheritance%20worth%20crores%2C%20their%20mother%20YS%20Vijayamma%20has%20written%20an%20open%20letter%2C%20putting%20her%20weight%20behind%20Ms%20Sharmila%20and%20saying%20that%20it's%20her%20%26quot%3Bduty%20to%20speak%20up%20for%20the%20unfairly%20treated%20child%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20released%20an%20open%20letter%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bmother%20has%20not%20been%20neutral%26quot%3B.%20The%20Jagan%20Reddy-led%20party%20said%20Vijayamma%20backed%20Sharmila%20and%20the%20Congress%20before%20and%20after%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20polls.%20In%20the%20state%20polls%20held%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20YSRCP%20suffered%20a%20rout%20and%20Jagan%20Reddy%20lost%20power%20to%20arch-rival%2C%20TDP's%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu.%20The%20YSRCP%20said%20YS%20Sharmila%20joined%20the%20party%20that%20had%20put%20Jagan%20Reddy%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20wrote%20that%20Sharmila%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20family%20business%20but%20worked%20selflessly%20in%20politics%20on%20Jagan%20Reddy's%20instructions.%20%26quot%3BJagan's%20rise%20to%20power%20owes%20much%20to%20Sharmila's%20efforts.%20As%20a%20mother%2C%20all%20children%20are%20equal.%20It's%20painful%20to%20see%20injustice%20done%20to%20one%20child.%20As%20a%20mother%2C%20it's%20my%20duty%20to%20speak%20up%20for%20the%20unfairly%20treated%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20Vijayamma%20wrote.%20She%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20painful%26quot%3B%20for%20her%20to%20watch%20these%20events%20unfold.%20%26quot%3BMy%20late%20husband%2C%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%2C%20our%20children%2C%20and%20I%20were%20a%20happy%20family.%20I'm%20unable%20to%20comprehend%20why%20our%20family%20is%20facing%20such%20difficulties.%20Despite%20my%20efforts%20to%20stop%20it%2C%20unfortunate%20events%20are%20unfolding%20before%20my%20eyes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijayamma%20slammed%20baseless%20claims%20being%20spread%20about%20her%20family%20and%20said%20this%20must%20stop.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20good%20for%20my%20children%2C%20nor%20for%20the%20state.%20I%20hesitated%20to%20bring%20this%20up%2C%20but%20the%20situation%20demands%20it.%20I%20implore%20those%20who%20have%20spoken%20wrongly%20about%20our%20family%20to%20cease.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBlood%20is%20thicker%20than%20water.%20My%20children%20will%20answer%20for%20themselves.%20I%20trust%20in%20God%2C%20who%20will%20provide%20solutions%20to%20their%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDismissing%20claims%20that%20YSR%20distributed%20his%20assets%20among%20his%20children%20while%20he%20was%20alive%2C%20she%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BYSR%20had%20transferred%20some%20assets%20to%20my%20younger%20daughter%2C%20Sharmila's%20name%2C%20and%20some%20to%20my%20son%2C%20Jagan's%20name%2C%20while%20he%20was%20alive.%20That's%20not%20dividing%20assets%3B%20it's%20just%20allocating%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYS%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%2C%20chief%20minister%20of%20undivided%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20a%20popular%20Congress%20leader%2C%20died%20in%20a%20helicopter%20crash%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYSR's%20wish%20was%20for%20his%20children%20to%20have%20equal%20shares%2C%20and%20that's%20the%20truth.%20Jagan%20worked%20hard%20to%20grow%20our%20assets%2C%20but%20all%20assets%20belong%20to%20the%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Vijayamma%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20YSR's%20untimely%20passing%20in%202009%2C%20Jagan%20and%20Sharmila%20lived%20together%20until%202019.%20Jagan%20gave%20Sharmila%20200%20crores%20from%20his%20share%20as%20per%20their%20agreement.%20According%20to%20the%20MoU%2C%20Jagan%20would%20get%2060%25%2C%20and%20Sharmila%2040%25.%20However%2C%20before%20the%20MoU%2C%20they%20shared%20equal%20dividends%20since%20Sharmila%20had%20an%20equal%20share%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijayamma%20wrote%20that%20Jagan%20Reddy%20proposed%20a%20division%20in%20assets%20after%20he%20became%20Chief%20Minister%20in%202019.%20She%20said%20he%20cited%20concerns%20about%20their%20grown%20children%20potentially%20not%20getting%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20that%2C%20in%20Vijayawada%2C%20in%20my%20presence%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20divide%20the%20assets%2C%20saying%20'this%20is%20Jagan's%20and%20this%20is%20Sharmila's'.%20The%20MoU%20written%20in%202019%20is%20the%20same%20one.%20This%20is%20the%20MoU%20written%20and%20signed%20by%20Jagan%20himself.%20Since%20Sharmila%20had%20rights%2C%20Jagan%20gave%20her%20200%20crores%20as%20dividends.%20Sharmila%20had%20rights%2C%20which%20is%20why%20they%20wrote%20the%20MoU.%20It%20was%20written%20officially.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20properties%20mentioned%20in%20the%20MoU%20to%20be%20given%20to%20Sharmila%20are%20not%20gifts%20from%20Jagan%20but%20his%20responsibility.%20Since%20there%20were%20no%20attachments%2C%20Jagan%20promised%20and%20signed%20that%20he%20would%20give%20Sharmila%20100%25%20of%20Saraswathi%20shares%20mentioned%20in%20the%20MoU%20and%20100%25%20of%20the%20Yelahanka%20property%20not%20mentioned%20in%20the%20MoU%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20Vijayamma%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSharmila%20was%20also%20unfairly%20treated%20regarding%20the%20unattached%20properties.%20Shaarmila's%20share%20included%20Bharati%20Cements%2C%20Sakshi%20Media%2C%20and%20YSR's%20house%2C%20which%20should%20be%20given%20after%20the%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0She%20said%20she%20had%20to%20speak%20up%20to%20clarify%20the%20truth%20%26quot%3Bamidst%20the%20falsehoods%20spread%20by%20many%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20truth%20is%20this...%20Still%2C%20they%20are%20siblings.%20This%20is%20their%20issue%3B%20they%20will%20resolve%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%20were%20alive%2C%20this%20asset%20issue%20wouldn't%20have%20arisen%2C%20and%20there%20wouldn't%20be%20such%20controversy.%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20had%20to%20speak%20out%20if%20it%20weren't%20for%20the%20ongoing%20chaos.%20I%20believe%20only%20my%20words%20can%20stop%20this.%20Please%2C%20I%20request%20you%20all%2C%20as%20my%20children%2C%20to%20refrain%20from%20speaking%20irresponsibly%2C%26quot%3B%20Vijayamma%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYSRCP%20responded%20to%20Vijayamma's%20letter%2C%20saying%20that%20Jagan%20Reddy%20never%20asked%20for%20the%20assets%20back.%20%26quot%3BYS%20Jagan%20has%20shared%20his%20assets%20with%20his%20sister%20Sharmila%20out%20of%20goodwill.%20She%20isn't%20a%20director%20in%20any%20of%20Jagan's%20businesses.%20Jagan%20treated%20Sharmila%20with%20kindness%2C%20just%20like%20any%20brother%20would.%20Late%20CM%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%20had%20already%20transferred%20assets%20to%20Sharmila%20and%20Jagan.%20Jagan%20never%20asked%20for%20those%20assets%20back.%20He%20only%20sent%20a%20notice%20regarding%20the%20exchange%20of%20attached%20properties%20in%20ED%20cases%20without%20his%20knowledge%2C%26quot%3B%20YSRCP%20state%20secretary%20SV%20Satish%20Reddy%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Siblings'%20Letter%20War%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20siblings%20have%20exchanged%20bitter%20letters%20amid%20the%20dispute%20and%20accused%20each%20other%20of%20%26quot%3Bdeceitful%20(and)%20deeply%20hurtful%26quot%3B%20actions%20that%20belittle%20their%20father's%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagan%20Reddy%20earlier%20wrote%20to%20the%20National%20Company%20Law%20Tribunal%20to%20red-flag%20the%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20transfer%20of%20shares%20in%20Saraswati%20Power.%20He%20said%20the%20shares%20were%20%26quot%3Bgiven%20to%20me%20in%20trust%20by%20a%20gift%20deed%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bgifted%26quot%3B%20them%20to%20their%20mother%2C%20YS%20Vijayalakshmi%2C%20%26quot%3Bwith%20the%20understanding%20that%20the%20transfer...%20would%20happen%20post%20court%20clearance%20(and)%20with%20execution%20of%20further%20appropriate%20documentation...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20shares%2C%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20wrote%2C%20had%20been%20transferred%20by%20his%20sister%20to%20herself%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeceitful%20manner%20(that)%20creates%20potential%20legal%20complications%20for%20me%26quot%3B.%20These%20shares%2C%20he%20said%2C%20would%20now%20%26quot%3Brevert%20to%20me%20as%20the%20original%20and%20continuing%20owner%20and%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20interest...%26quot%3B%20The%20YSR%20Congress%20boss%20also%20declared%20void%20the%20MoU%20he%20signed%20in%202019.%20The%20MoU%20mentioned%20his%20intention%20%26quot%3Bto%20effect%20transfer%20of%20certain%20properties%20to%20you...%20out%20of%20my%20love%20and%20affection%20for%20you%20as%20my%20sibling%2C%20at%20a%20point%20of%20time%20in%20future%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Ms%20Sharmila%20flagged%20their%20father's%20%26quot%3Bunambiguous%26quot%3B%20instruction%20%26quot%3Bthat%20all%20properties%20acquired%20with%20family%20resources%20during%20his%20lifetime%20should%20be%20divided%20equally%20between%20his%20four%20grandchildren%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20dismissed%20Jagan%20Reddy's%20intention%20to%20scrap%20the%20MoU%2C%20saying%20it%20has%20no%20legal%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20done%20what%20our%20dear%20father%20would%20never%20have%20imagined...%20filed%20cases%20against%20his%20dear%20wife%20(our%20mother)%20and%20daughter%20(myself)%20to%20deprive%20his%20family%20of%20their%20legitimate%20share%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20vexed%20issue%20of%20Saraswati%20Power%20shares%2C%20Ms%20Reddy%20claimed%20the%20intention%20had%20been%20to%20transfer%20on%20signing%20of%20the%20MoU%20%26quot%3Bbut%20you%20(Jagan%20Reddy)%20failed%20to%20fulfill%20this%20promise%20for%20several%20years...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20law%20tribunal%20will%20be%20hearing%20the%20matter%20on%20November%208.%3C%