nd-jeh-jet-off-for-a-vacay-on-diwali-jeh-gets-all-the-attention-yet-again-watch-video%2Farticleshow%2F114762228.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rs%2015%20Crore%20Ransom%20Demand%20In%20Delhi%20Firing%20Case%2C%20Orders%20Came%20From%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20sharp-shooters%20linked%20to%20the%20Kaushal%20Chaudhary-Bambiha%20gang%20were%20arrested%20for%20opening%20fire%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20a%20businessman%20in%20Delhi%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%20Bilal%20Ansari%2C%2022%2C%20and%20Shuheb%20Qureshi%2C%2021%2C%20both%20natives%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Bulandshahr%2C%20were%20arrested%20during%20a%20shootout%2C%20three%20days%20after%20they%20carried%20out%20the%20shooting%20in%20North%20West%20Delhi's%20Rani%20Bagh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20accused%2C%20who%20were%20on%20a%20bike%2C%20fired%20multiple%20rounds%20to%20extort%20Rs%2015%20crore%20from%20the%20Delhi%20businessman%20and%20left%20a%20slip%20bearing%20the%20name%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BKaushal%20Chaudhary%20-%20Pawan%20Shokeen%20-%20Bambhia%20Gang.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20interrogation%2C%20they%20told%20the%20police%20that%20gangster%20Pawan%20Shaukeen%2C%20who%20has%20fled%20from%20India%20and%20is%20currently%20operating%20from%20the%20US%2C%20had%20ordered%20them%20to%20open%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Pawan%20Shaukeen%20Hired%20The%20Shooters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawan%20Shaukeen%2C%20who%20was%20an%20arms%20supplier%20in%20Delhi%2C%20met%20one%20of%20the%20shooters%2C%20Bilal%2C%20when%20he%20was%20working%20in%20a%20factory%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesg's%20Khurja%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20contacted%20him%20and%20asked%20to%20do%20a%20recce%20of%20the%20residence%20of%20the%20businessman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawan%20also%20told%20him%20he%20would%20be%20paid%20for%20the%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilal%20then%20contacted%20Shuheb%2C%20whom%20he%20had%20met%20through%20a%20common%20friend%20who%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20Pawan%20Shokeen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gangster%20told%20both%20to%20fire%20upon%20the%20residence%20in%20the%20Rani%20Bagh%20area.%20While%20Shuheb%20was%20driving%20the%20bike%2C%20Bilal%20carried%20out%20the%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERise%20Of%20Extortion%20Bids%20In%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20has%20witnessed%20a%20spate%20of%20firing%20incidents%20as%20part%20of%20extortion%20attempts%20in%20the%20past%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20three%20sensational%20incidents%20of%20firing%20occurred%20in%20the%20capital%20--%20at%20a%20car%20showroom%20in%20Naraina%20in%20west%20Delhi%2C%20a%20hotel%20in%20southwest%20Delhi%20and%20the%20sweet%20shop%2C%20all%20were%20linked%20to%20extortion%20activities%20by%20gangsters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20incident%2C%20shots%20were%20fired%20at%20a%20second-hand%20car%20showroom%20called%20'Car%20Street%20Mini'%20in%20southwest%20Delhi's%20Naraina%2C%20barely%20a%20kilometre%20from%20the%20Naraina%20police%20station.%20Officials%20said%20at%20least%2020%20rounds%20were%20fired%20by%20three%20men%20who%20entered%20the%20showroom%2C%20causing%20panic%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shooters%20left%20behind%20a%20slip%2C%20reading%20%26quot%3BBhau%20Gang%2C%20Since%202020%26quot%3B.%20The%20%26quot%3BBhau%20Gang%26quot%3B%20mention%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20reference%20to%20wanted%20gangster%20Himanshu%20Bhau%2C%20who%20fled%20the%20country%20in%202022%20and%20is%20currently%20believed%20to%20be%20in%20Portugal.%20He%20had%20also%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20man%20at%20a%20food%20outlet%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20a%20similar%20shooting%20was%20carried%20out%20at%20a%20car%20showroom%20in%20West%20Delhi's%20Tilak%20Nagar%20and%20the%20same%20gang%20was%20suspected%20to%20be%20behind%20the%20attack.%20Sources