2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20entered%20university%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20manage%20to%20get%20into%20any%20law%20schools%20in%20Singapore%20because%20I%20didn't%20do%20well%20enough%20for%20my%20A%20Level%20examinations.%20Instead%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20to%20business%20school%2C%20where%20I%20developed%20an%20interest%20in%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20was%20given%20the%20chance%20to%20take%20a%20second%20degree%20in%20law%20after%20doing%20well%20in%20my%20freshman%20year.%20I%20took%20up%20the%20offer%2C%20and%20that's%20how%20I%20ended%20up%20doing%20two%20degrees%20as%20an%20undergraduate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20it%20was%20a%20blessing%20in%20disguise%20that%20I%20didn't%20get%20into%20law%20school%20earlier.%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20discovered%20finance%20%E2%80%94%20which%20I'm%20more%20interested%20in%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dcfe27a8-d609-42d9-b584-282e8e48f476%5C%22%3ELanding%20a%20job%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bmagic%20circle%26quot%3B%20law%20firm%20and%20an%20internship%20with%20a%20top%20US%20bank%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202023%2C%20I%20received%20a%20training%20contract%20offer%20from%20one%20of%20the%20UK's%20top%20five%20law%20firms%2C%20also%20known%20as%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flatham-watkins-us-law-firm-poaching-top-uk-lawyers-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emagic%20circle%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20people%2C%20that%20would%20have%20spelled%20the%20end%20of%20one's%20job%20hunt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20wasn't%20the%20case%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20also%20in%20the%20running%20for%20a%20summer%20internship%20with%20a%20US%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboutique-investment-banks-vs-bulge-brackets-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebulge%20bracket%20bank%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20secured%20that%20investment%20