er-podcast-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eepisode%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20The%20Verge's%20%26quot%3BDecoder%26quot%3B%20podcast%2C%20released%20Monday%2C%20the%20Airbnb%20CEO%20explained%20what%20people%20are%20misunderstanding%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20%26quot%3Bfounder%20mode%26quot%3B%20was%20popularized%20in%20September%20by%20Y%20Combinator%20founding%20partner%20Paul%20Graham%2C%20who%20wrote%20that%20Chesky%20inspired%20it.%20Graham%20said%20that%20founders%20were%20too%20often%20working%20in%20%26quot%3Bmanager%20mode%26quot%3B%20while%20running%20their%20companies%20rather%20than%20getting%20involved%20in%20the%20nitty-gritty%20like%20they%20typically%20do%20in%20a%20company's%20early%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20all%2C%20people%20don't%20know%20what%20founder%20mode%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Chesky%20said%20on%20the%20podcast.%20%26quot%3BThey%20think%20it%20means%20swagger.%20I%20remember%20a%20tweet%20that%20said%2C%20'I'm%20going%20founder%20mode%20on%20this%20burrito.'%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20that%20means.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbnb-ceo-brian-chesky%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChesky%2C%20who%20cofounded%20Airbnb%20in%202007%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0says%2C%20%26quot%3BThat%20wasn't%20the%20message.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20could%20summarize%20founder%20mode%20in%20a%20couple%20sentences%2C%20it's%20about%20being%20in%20the%20details%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20that%20great%20leadership%20is%20presence%2C%20not%20absence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20echoed%20a%20warning%20that%20other%20tech%20leaders%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-might-cut-metas-middle-management-report-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20famously%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20issued%20about%20organizational%20bloat%20and%20extraneous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%