%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20make%20smart%20decisions%20with%20my%20money.%20Once%20I%20built%20up%20my%20savings%20account%2C%20emergency%20savings%20account%2C%20and%20retirement%20fund%2C%20I%20decided%20it%20was%20time%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-invest-in-stocks%5C%22%3Einvest%20in%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20buying%20stock%20in%20random%20companies%20I%20was%20interested%20in%20and%20before%20I%20knew%20it%2C%20I%20had%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars%20invested%20in%20over%2020%20individual%20companies.%20That%20was%20a%20big%20mistake.%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20I%20was%20doing%2C%20and%20wasn't%20keeping%20up%20with%20the%20market%20to%20know%20when%20to%20buy%20more%20or%20sell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20move%20away%20from%20investing%20in%20individual%20stocks%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20put%20money%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-invest-in-index-funds%5C%22%3Elow-cost%20index%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20mutual%20funds.%20The%20problem%20was%2C%20it%20seemed%20too%20confusing%20to%20even%20know%20where%20to%20begin.%20That's%20why%20I%20asked%20financial%20experts%20to%20explain%20the%20main%20differences%20between%20index%20funds%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fmutual-funds%5C%22%3Emutual%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Here's%20what%20they%20had%20to%20say.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20An%20index%20fund%20%3Cem%3Ecan%3C%2Fem%3E%20be%20a%20mutual%20fund%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20it%20might%20sound%20confusing%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fclaytonbwood%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClayton%20Wood%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20financial%20planner%2C%20says%20a%20good%20first%20step%20is%20understanding%20that%20an%20index%20fund%20is%20a%20mutual%20fund%2C%20but%20a%20mutual%20fund%20is%20not%20always%20an%20index%20fund.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20mutual%20fund%20is%20the%20pooling%20of%20money%20from%20multiple%20sources%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20bucket%20of%20investments%20usually%20managed%20by%20an%20asset%20manager%2C%26quot%3Bsays%20Wood.%20%26quot%3BA%20mutual%20fund's%20investments%20are%20guided%20by%20its%20Investment%20Objectives%2C%20which%20are%20found%20in%20the%20prospectus%20of%20the%20fund.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20is%20an%20index%20fund%20different%20from%20a%20mutual%20fund%3F%20Wood%20says%20that%20an%20index%20fund%20is%20the%20pooling%20of%20money%20that%20invests%20in%20a%20portfolio%20that%20tracks%20an%20index%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-the-sp-500%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThe%20investment%20objective%20of%20the%20index%20fund%20is%20to%20mirror%20the%20investments%20and%20allocations%20of%20the%20index%20that%20is%20chosen%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Wood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20Index%20funds%20have%20lower%20expenses%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20fees%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdistrictcapitalmanagement.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlvin%20Carlos%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20financial%20planner%2C%20says%20that%20index%20funds%20are%20low-cost%20mutual%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20Costco%20of%20investing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Carlos.%20%26quot%3BIndex%20fund%20fees%20can%20be%2010x%20lower%20than%20an%20averagely-priced%20mutual%20fund.%20Also%2C%20Index%20funds%20can%20give%20you%20better%20returns%20compared%20to%20a%20mutual%20fund.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStudies%20show%20that%20you%20can%20make%20more%20money%20by%20investing%20in%20low-fee%20index%20funds%20compared%20to%20higher-fee%20mutual%20funds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BMore%20than%2082%25%20of%20mutual%20