ed%20by%20law%20to%20make%20capital%20gains%20distributions%20to%20shareholders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20distribution%20represents%20the%20net%20gains%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20the%20investments%20throughout%20the%20year%20in%20the%20fund%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BSince%20ETFs%20are%20typically%20passive%20investments%20that%20track%20an%20index%2C%20an%20investor%20typically%20does%20not%20realize%20a%20taxable%20event%20until%20they%20sell%20their%20investment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdifferences-index-mutual-funds-finally-know-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730231725000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6206d6db3b86990018b30706%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdifferences-index-mutual-funds-finally-know-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Have%20you%20ever%20found%20yourself%20wondering%20about%20the%20difference%20between%20index%20and%20mutual%20funds%3F%20Here%20are%20five%20differences%20explained%20by%20financial%20planners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jen%20Glantz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdifferences-index-mutual-funds-finally-know-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Natasa%20attends%20Diwali%20bash%20with%20Aleksandar%20Alex%3A%20Video%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730230711000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114745901%2Cimgsize-67894.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fnatasa-stankovic-makes-a-stylish-diwali-appearance-with-aleksandar-alex-ami