f%20Tzurit%20Or%20opened%20the%20first%20Tatte%20location%20in%20Brookline%2C%20Massachusetts.%20(%26quot%3BTatte%26quot%3B%20is%20Yiddish%20for%20%26quot%3Bpapa.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETatte%20really%20began%20expanding%20outside%20of%20the%20greater%20Boston%20area%20after%20investor%20Ron%20Shaich%20purchased%20over%2050%25%20of%20its%20ownership%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20Scaich%20%E2%80%94%20nicknamed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bigshot.show%2Fron-shaich%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Godfather%20of%20Fast%20Casual%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20has%20a%20pretty%20stacked%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20as%20the%20cofounder%20and%20former%20CEO%20of%20Panera%20Bread%2C%20cofounder%20of%20Au%20Bon%20Pain%2C%20and%20a%20lead%20investor%20of%20Cava.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETatte%20headed%20southward%20in%20August%202020%20with%20its%20first%20location%20in%20DC's%20West%20End%20neighborhood%20and%20it%20now%20has%20over%2040%20caf%C3%A9s%20throughout%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-boston-hated-it-loved-massachusetts-suburbs-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMassachusetts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20greater%20DC%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20chain%20is%20more%20than%20just%20a%20bakery%20and%20caf%C3%A9.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Counter%20of%20baked%20goods%20behind%20glass%20at%20subway-tiled%20covered%20bakery%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671a7d0a9b3250dbbce9ccb0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETatte's%20display%20case%20of%20desserts%20and%20baked%20goods%20is%20eye-catching.%20%3Cp%3EAlice%20Levitt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20intricately%20tiled%20floors%2C%20shiny%20subway-tile%20walls%2C%20and%20caf%C3%A9%20tables%20that%20can%20barely%20withstand%20the%20heft%20of%20what%20I%20insist%20on%20ordering%2C%20the%20locations%20have%20a%20relatively%20uniform%20vibe%20that%20immediately%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BTatte.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20offers%20a%20wide%20selection%20of%20baked%20goods%2C%20plus%20brunch%20dishes%2C%20sandwiches%2C%20salads%2C%20and%20other%20fast-casual%20bites.%20It's%20perhaps%20best%20to%20think%20of%20the%20flavors%20on%20offer%20as%20having%20Israeli%2C%20Mediterranean%2C%20American%2C%20and%20European%20influences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20dishes%20feel%20American%20with%20a%20twist%20(bacon%2C%20lettuce%2C%20avocado%2C%20and%20tomato%20on%20challah%20bread)%2C%20but%20others%20seem%20more%20explicitly%20Israeli%20(lamb%20kebab%20with%20baba%20ghanoush).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFusion%20comes%20in%20the%20form%20of%20selections%20like%20a%20harissa-maple-glazed%20short%20rib%20served%20over%20eggplant%20and%20couscous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EStill%2C%20dessert%20is%20the%20best%20part%20of%20a%20visit%20to%20Tatte.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Glass%20display%20case%20of%20desserts%20at%20Tatte%20bakery%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671a7e59a0a0cc14f2239fe8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20dessert%20case%20is%20often%20filled%20with%20tempting%20treats.%20%3Cp%3EAlice%20Levitt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20centerpiece%20of%20the%20store%20is%20always%20the%20bakery%20counter%2C%20which%20I%20never%20pass%20without%20grabbing%20a%20halva%20brownie%20or%20pistachio%20croissant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20often%20packed%20with%20a%20range%20of%20sweet%20and%20savory%20laminated-dough%20treats%20from%20flaky%20kouign-amanns%20to%20chocolate%20snails%2C%20all%20awaiting%20discovery%20among%20other%20non-refrigerated%20delights%20like%20the%20halva%20chocolate-chunk%20cookie%20and%20monkey%20bread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20refrigerated%20case%20is%20usually%20filled%20with%20desserts%20ranging%20from%20fruity%20to%20chocolaty.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Franked-every-flavor-at-the-cheesecake-factory-worst-to-best-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeesecake%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20especially%20noteworthy%2C%20topped%20with%20a%20selection%20of%20different%20berries%20arranged%20by%20color.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20never%20skip%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%20here.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Latte%20with%20heart-shaped%20art%20in%20it%20next%20to%20two%20desserts%20on%20small%20white%20plates%20with%20spoons%20on%20marble%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671a7dcb01ea6d83dee3caa1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETatte's%20pistachio%20latte%20is%20made%20with%20a%20delicious%20syrup.%20%3Cp%3EAlice%20Levitt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20patently%20not%20a%20coffee%20drinker%20%E2%80%94%20even%20the%20most%20insipid%20versions%20have%20always%20been%20too%20bitter%20for%20me.%20But%20I%20am%20one%20when%20at%20Tatte%2C%20where%20I%20love%20to%20have%20a%20few%20sips%20of%20my%20husband's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-starbucks-pistachio-latte-review-winter-menu-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epistachio%20latte%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latte%20is%20made%20with%20house-roasted%20espresso%20that%20tastes%20like%20chocolate%20and%20caramel%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20house-made%20pistachio%20syrup%20that's%20captured%20my%20fancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20pity%20to%20see%20the%20skillful%20latte%20art%20dissipate%20with%20each%20sip%2C%20but%20there%20are%20rewards%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20cup.%20The%20thick%2C%20slightly%20chunky%20syrup%20collects%20at%20the%20bottom%2C%20leaving%20a%20few%20final%20super-powered%20pistachio%20sips.%20I%20love%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20my%20husband%20says%20it's%20like%20%26quot%3Bchewable%20coffee.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20shakshuka%20has%20always%20been%20my%20favorite.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Small%20pot%20of%20sauce%2C%20feta%2C%20tomatoes%20next%20to%20toasted%20bread%20on%20cutting%20board%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671a7e2c01ea6d83dee3cabe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETatte's%20shakshuka%20is%20served%20with%20crispy%20bread.%20%3Cp%3EAlice%20Levitt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20the%20diverse%20greater%20DC%20area%2C%20I've%20had%20trouble%20finding%20a%20truly%20great%20version%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-ina-garten-new-egg-recipe-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eegg%20dish%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20popular%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20North%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20I%20found%20Tatte's%20shakshuka.%20There%2C%20the%20oversize%20pan%20filled%20with%20tomato%2C%20pepper%2C%20and%20onion%20sauce%20is%20always%20picture-perfect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20favorite%20version%20of%20the%20dish%20on%20the%20menu%20has%20lamb%20meatballs%20and%20labneh.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20crimson%20base%2C%20soft-centered%20eggs%20break%20to%20make%20the%20sauce%20creamier%20and%20even%20more%20enjoyable.%20The%20oblong%20lamb%20meatballs%20are%20spiced%20just%20enough%20to%20supply%20a%20taste%20of%20Israel%20that%20combines%20harmoniously%20with%20the%20blobs%20of%20spicy%20labneh%20(strained%20yogurt)%20and%20fresh%20parsley.%20The%20unexpected%20star%20of%20the%20show%20for%20me%20is%20the%20sweet%20and%20lightly%20spicy%20peppadew%20peppers%20on%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dish%20comes%20with%20three%20slices%20of%20toasted%20challah%20for%20sopping%20up%20every%20last%20clump%20of%20tomato%20and%20pepper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20husband%20prefers%20the%20house%20breakfast%20plate.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hashbrown%20topped%20with%20seasoning%20with%20bacon%2C%20egg%2C%20toast%2C%20sauce%20on%20oval%20plate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671a7e4301ea6d83dee3cac3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20potato%20fritters%20are%20one%20of%20the%20best%20parts%20of%20this%20dish.%20%3Cp%3EAlice%20Levitt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Tatte%2C%20my%20husband%20goes%20for%20a%20classic%20breakfast%20with%20toast%2C%20potato%20fritters%2C%20and%20crispy%20bacon%20paired%20with%20eggs%20cooked%20how%20you%20like.%20Diners%20can%20also%20add%20beef%20sausage%20to%20the%20dish.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20potato%20fritters%20are%20a%20highlight%20%E2%80%94%20two%20crispy%20latkes%20served%20beneath%20a%20dusting%20of%20Parmesan%20cheese%20with%20flecks%20of%20mint%2C%20along%20with%20tomato%20jam%20for%20dipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETatte's%20dessert%20offerings%20have%20impressed%20me.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Passion-fruit%20curd%20topped%20pastry%20next%20to%20one%20topped%20with%20glazed%20chocolate%20ganache%20on%20white%20plates%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671aac56a0a0cc14f223c39e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20ordered%20the%20passionfruit%20krembo%20and%20halva%20bomb%20at%20Tatte.%20%3Cp%3EAlice%20Levitt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20rarely%20repeat%20a%20dessert%20at%20Tatte.%20Not%20because%20I%20tire%20of%20them%2C%20but%20because%20there%20are%20so%20many%20I%20want%20to%20try.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20this%20visit%2C%20I%20went%20with%20the%20passionfruit%20krembo%20and%20halva%20bomb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKrembos%20are%20a%20popular%20treat%20in%20Israel%20that%20are%20similar%20to%20a%20chocolate%20teacake%20or%20Mallomar.%20They're%20essentially%20soft%20cookies%20topped%20with%20a%20pile%20of%20marshmallow%20fluff%20enrobed%20in%20chocolate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20passionfruit%20krembo%20at%20Tatte%20takes%20the%20dessert%20to%20new%20heights%20by%20mixing%20passionfruit%20curd%20with%20vanilla%20meringue.%20The%20combination%20of%20textures%20and%20flavors%20made%20me%20go%20back%20for%20bite%20after%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20just%20as%20impressed%20with%20the%20halva%20bomb%2C%20which%20wasn't%20too%20sweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20growing%20up%2C%20my%20father%20was%20an%20avowed%20halva%20eater%2C%20but%20I%20was%20always%20turned%20off%20by%20the%20dense%2C%20clay-like%20bars%20of%20it%20he'd%20buy%20at%20the%20supermarket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20sesame%20paste%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20halva%20bomb%20I%20ordered%20was%20soft%20and%20vanilla-scented%2C%20covered%20in%20whipped%20milk-chocolate%20ganache%20and%20a%20dark-chocolate-ganache%20glaze.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20would%20love%20to%20see%20Tatte%20expand%20throughout%20the%20US.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20photo%20of%20shakshuka%2C%20two%20pastries%2C%20latte%2C%20and%20English%20breakfast%20platter%20on%20white%20marble%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671a7e73a0a0cc14f2239fec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20spread%20at%20Tatte%20cost%20over%20%2450.%20%3Cp%3ETyson%20Bateman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20party%20of%20two%20spent%20%2450.50%20before%20tax%20and%20tip%2C%20which%20seemed%20like%20a%20fair%20price%20for%20two%20meals%2C%20a%20coffee%2C%20and%20two%20desserts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20again%2C%20I'd%20left%20Tatte%20feeling%20impressed%20and%20wishing%20the%20chain%20was%20expanding%20around%20the%20US%20quicker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brand%20is%20still%20only%20available%20in%20Boston%20and%20the%20DC%20Metro%20area%2C%20with%20its%20second%20Mary