0unsure%20of%20how%20therapy%20would%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20was%20soon%20diagnosed%20with%20clinical%20anxiety%20and%20gradually%20realised%20that%20seeking%20help%20was%20okay.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20way%20out.%20I%20understood%20that%20this%20is%20real%2C%20and%20instead%20of%20fighting%20it%2C%20I%20accepted%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nikhil%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202017%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20break%20and%20quit%20YRF.%20%E2%80%9CI%20owed%20it%20to%20myself.%E2%80%9D%20He%20acknowledges%20his%20privilege%20in%20being%20able%20to%20do%20so%2C%20as%20his%20wife%20was%20working%20at%20the%20time%20and%20he%20had%20savings%20to%20fall%20back%20on.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERedefining%20masculinity%3A%20%E2%80%98Be%20a%20man%2C%20%3Cem%3Eyaar%3C%2Fem%3E!%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20returned%20home%20to%20his%20parents%20in%20Bahrain%20and%20spent%20time%20with%20loved%20ones.%20He%20engaged%20in%20activities%20he%20loved%20%E2%80%94%20travelling%2C%20reconnecting%20with%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20and%20reigniting%20lost%20connections.%20He%20changed%20his%20phone%20number%20and%20effectively%20switched%20off%20from%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20biggest%20learnings%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20breaking%20free%20from%20the%20societal%20definitions%20of%20masculinity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20story%20reflects%20the%20conditioning%20of%20masculinity%20that%20many%20boys%20in%20our%20country%20experience.%20Everything%20is%20linked%20to%20money%20and%20providing.%20We%20never%20take%20time%20to%20find%20joy%20in%20life.%20Historically%2C%20men%20have%20been%20viewed%20as%20providers%20and%20women%20are%20seen%20as%20nurturers.%20Today%2C%20while%20women%20play%20both%20roles%2C%20men%20are%20stil