E2%80%99t%20go%20back%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Ejhuggi-jhopdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2021%2C%20Rahim%E2%80%99s%20life%20tells%20a%20different%20story.%20He%E2%80%99s%20running%20a%20successful%20aquarium%20cleaning%20business%20and%20is%20pursuing%20paramedic%20and%20lab%20technician%20courses.%20He%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20learning%20how%20to%20invest%3B%20he%20is%20also%20sending%20money%20home%20to%20support%20his%20ageing%20mother%20and%20sister.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20even%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359592%2Flinkedin-for-blue-collar-daily-wager-labourer-digital-labour-chowk-job-search-migrant-workers-bihar-uttar-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20providing%20jobs%20to%20others%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20same%20programme%20that%20helped%20him.%20Rahim%20is%20one%20of%20175%20youth%20whose%20lives%20have%20been%20transformed%20by%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3EWeLive%20Foundation%2C%20an%20aftercare%20facility%20that%20empowers%20young%20adults%20who%20have%20aged%20out%20of%C2%A0%20childcare%20institutions%20(CCIs).%20It%20offers%20them%20more%20than%20just%20shelter%20%E2%80%94%20it%20gives%20them%20dignity%2C%20purpose%2C%20and%20a%20path%20to%20self-reliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemember%20the%20first%20time%20you%20stepped%20out%20of%20your%20home%2C%20unsure%20of%20which%20college%20course%20to%20pick%2C%20struggling%20to%20find%20that%20first%20job%2C%20or%20save%20enough%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20space%20in%20a%20new%20city%3F%20Adulting%20is%20tough%20%E2%80%94%20filled%20with%20confusion%2C%20complexity%2C%20and%20countless%20moments%20of%20self-discovery.%20Now%2C%20imagine%20navigating%20this%20transition%20without%20a%20family%20or%20support%20system%2C%20often%20with%20the%20added%20burden%20of%20emotional%2C%20physical%2C%20or%20even%20sexual%20trauma.%20This%20is%20the%20reality%20for%20thousands%20of%20youth%20who%20are%20forced%20to%20