2%80%99t%20feel%20good%20from%20within%2C%20it%20can%20be%20incredibly%20hard%20for%20them%20to%20hold%20down%20a%20job%20or%20excel%20in%20their%20studies%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramya%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelonging%20to%20the%20age%20group%20of%2018%20to%2023%2C%20these%20young%20care%20leavers%20from%20about%2010-12%20states%20of%20India%20are%20open%20to%20stay%20at%20the%20facility%20for%202-3%20years%20until%20they%20gain%20some%20work%20experience%2C%20education%20and%20savings%20to%20get%20back%20on%20their%20feet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamya%2C%20recalling%20the%20earlier%20days%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20shared%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20first%20started%2C%20our%20focus%20was%20on%20improving%20work%20readiness.%20It%20seemed%20straightforward%20%E2%80%94%20getting%20the%20youth%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F272114%2Fautobot-india-academy-provides-jobs-for-electric-vehicle-engineers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskilling%20and%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20streams%2C%20and%20helping%20them%20secure%20jobs.%20However%2C%20ensuring%20they%20stayed%20in%20these%20jobs%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20challenge.%20Many%2C%20like%20most%20of%20us%2C%20switch%20two%20or%20three%20jobs%20before%20settling%2C%20and%20guiding%20them%20through%20this%20process%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20support.%20Once%20we%20established%20partnerships%20with%20skill%20providers%20and%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20help%20them%20stick%20with%20their%20jobs%2C%20things%20began%20to%20fall%20into%20place.%E2%80%99%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20culture%20of%20saving%20and%20investing%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3C