p%20them%20recognise%20the%20influence%20their%20relationships%20have%20on%20their%20emotional%20health%2C%20and%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20connection%20or%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20challenging%20one%2C%20it%20all%20plays%20a%20part%20in%20their%20growth%20and%20healing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20always%20the%20first%20job%20which%20is%20the%20hardest%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnly%20about%20one-third%20of%20our%20youth%20are%20enrolled%20in%20graduate%20programmes.%20Most%20are%20still%20striving%20to%20complete%20their%2010th%20or%2012th%20grades%2C%20which%20makes%20entering%20the%20workforce%20particularly%20daunting.%20Just%20imagine%20stepping%20into%20the%20world%20at%2018%20without%20a%2010th-grade%20qualification%20%E2%80%94%20so%20many%20entry-level%20positions%20become%20inaccessible.%20This%20leaves%20them%20vulnerable%2C%20often%20relegated%20to%20gig%20work%20or%20restaurant%20jobs%20that%20can%20lead%20to%20exploitation.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20be%20their%20safety%20net%2C%20providing%20a%20cushion%20and%20the%20right%20encouragement%20to%20help%20them%20build%20their%20skills%20and%20step%20confidently%20into%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamya%20recalls%20a%20poignant%20success%20story%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20girl%20who%20joined%20us%20%E2%80%94%20extremely%20talented%20but%20struggling%20to%20find%20a%20job.%20We%20soon%20realised%20that%20something%20deeper%20was%20holding%20her%20back%2C%20something%20that%20had%20shattered%20her%20confidence%20and%20self-esteem.%20For%20six%20months%2C%20we%20worked%20closely%20with%20her%2C%20providing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337049%2Fitc-fiama-mental-health-survey-therapy-counselling-support-gen-z-millennials-parents%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecounselling%20and%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20