264065%2Fwhat-is-invisible-disability-workplace-autism-depression-adhd-policy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoping%20strategies%20he%20employs%20at%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20also%20offers%20valuable%20insights%20for%20others%20with%20ADHD%20navigating%20the%20workspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20experiencing%20difficulties%20with%20attention%20throughout%20his%20life%2C%20Aalen%20sought%20help%20for%20anxiety%20three%20years%20ago%20and%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20something%20known%20as%20executive%20dysfunction%2C%20and%20I%20learnt%20about%20it%20very%20late%20in%20life.%20It%E2%80%99s%20like%20a%20mental%20block%20essentially.%20If%20there%20is%20something%20that%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20do%2C%20I%20simply%20cannot%20do%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20procrastination%3B%20I%20know%20I%20have%20to%20do%20it%2C%20but%20I%20cannot.%20Many%20people%20with%20ADHD%20struggle%20with%20deadlines%20and%20submitting%20assignments%20due%20to%20this%20reason.%20The%20brain%20just%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20function%20that%20way.%20Another%20problem%20I%20have%20is%20difficulty%20with%20attention%20to%20detail%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CADHD%20can%20often%20be%20identified%20in%20childhood%20or%20adolescence%2C%20and%20while%20it%20is%20manageable%2C%20getting%20diagnosed%20after%20entering%20the%20workforce%20can%20bring%20additional%20challenges.%20Adults%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD%20may%20experience%20heightened%20anger%2C%20stress%2C%20and%20relationship%20issues%2C%20alongside%20reduced%20dynamism%20and%20good%20spirit%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pompa%20Maitra%20Chakraborty%2C%20a%20clinical%20psychologist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5