s%20keep%20my%20earphones%20handy%2C%20which%20helps%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aalen%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20540px)%20100vw%2C%20540px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-17-at-23.36.00-1-1-1729686729.jpeg%3Ffit%3D500%252C645%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aalen%20Isaac%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-17-at-23.36.00-1-1-1729686729.jpeg%3Fw%3D540%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20540w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-17-at-23.36.00-1-1-1729686729.jpeg%3Fresize%3D232%252C300%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20232w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-17-at-23.36.00-1-1-1729686729.jpeg%3Fresize%3D500%252C645%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-17-at-23.36.00-1-1-1729686729.jpeg%3Fresize%3D150%252C194%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371952%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22697%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAalen%20suggests%20that%20regular%20exercise%20can%20improve%20focus%20and%20productivity%20for%20individuals%20with%20ADHD%20in%20the%20workplace%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20primary%20forces%20driving%20Aalen%20in%20his%20career%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Ftop-mental-health-expert-do-you-need-help-get-free-counselling-find-support-manage-stress-more%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresence%20of%20stress%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CDeadlines%20trigger%20significant%20anxiety%20for%20me%2