oint%20pains%2C%20but%20these%20days%2C%20even%20young%20people%20and%20toddlers%20are%20experiencing%20blood%20glucose%20issues.%20I%20am%20not%20an%20expert%2C%20but%20I%20believe%20everything%20is%20related%20to%20the%20food%20we%20eat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C628%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jitender%20and%20Sarla%20have%20developed%20a%20profitable%20venture%20by%20selling%20moringa%20powder.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C402%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-16-1729263026.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C79%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20data-recalc-dims%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371317%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJitender%20and%20Sarla%20have%20developed%20a%20profitable%20venture%20by%20selling%20moringa%20powder.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20an%20ICMR%20(Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research)%20report%20had%20revealed%20that%20an%20estimated%2056.4%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20disease%20burden%20was%20linked%20to%20unhealthy%20diets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJitender%E2%80%99s%20realisation%20fueled%20his%20determination%20to%20move%20back%20to%20his%20ancestral%20home%20in%20Mehmudpur%20village%20in%20Sonipat%20district%20of%20Haryana%2C%20alongside%20his%20wife%2C%20Sarla.%20In%202018%2C%20after%20working%20for%2011%20years%20at%20Tata%20Consultancy%20Services%20(TCS)%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20become%20a%20farmer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20gradually%20explored%20the%20healing%20properties%20of%20moringa%20and%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20to%20promote%20its%20potential%20health%20benefits.%20Today%2C%20they%20have%20developed%20a%20profitable%20venture%20by%20selling%20moringa%20powder%20to%20urban%20consumers%20in%20cities%20like%20Delhi%2C%20Gurugram%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETapping%20into%20%E2%80%98miraculous%20benefits%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%202015%2C%20during%20his%20stay%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Jitender%20first%20started%20growing%20moringa%20on%20the%20terrace%20of%20his%20home.%20%E2%80%9CI%20developed%20a%20lush%20green%20garden%20with%20vegetables%20such%20as%20ridge%20gourd%2C%20bottle%20gourd%2C%20and%20moringa%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jitender%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImpressed%20by%20the%20results%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20replace%20their%20wheat%20and%20paddy%20fields%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F303221%2Fkerala-engineer-turned-farmer-starts-moringa-mango-organic-farm-in-melbourne-australia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%